Quicksnap Use Cases

UC01 Start program
UC02 End program
UC03 Set home directory
UC04 Take full screenshot
UC05 Take partial screenshot
UC06 Save images locally:
	Save the last X (3) number of pictures in a temp directory, unless save is toggled during or after screenshot
UC07 View image:
	Show the default save directory in a side panel, where the selected image is displayed in the image view.
UC08 Upload to imagesharing host
UC09 Specify an imagesharing host
UC10 Forget link

UCX1 Drawing on pictures before uploading